{"tid":1606942,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"未fc 轉自fb：黑警徵用各區體育館，今晚通宵運作。","createTime":"2019-09-30T16:40:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T17:33:39.000Z","uid":23707,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9edd7f521b30baf3850fb9923ec93e03ff0042af","tid":1606942,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:40:39.000Z","msg":"[轉]<br />\n<br />\n關於10.1 事態嚴重，以防萬一，決定公開這個post.<br />\n<br />\n兩位都是很好的朋友，沒有可能對我講大話。<br />\n請各位注意，打醒十二分精神！<br />\n<br />\n我本人的一位好朋友，他身邊的朋友大部份都是康文處職員：「警察開始徵用各區體育館，今晚通宵運作。大家留意。」<br />\n可以的話，多加留意自己屋苑附近的體育館。電話裡面講的，所以不會有對話給大家看。20190930 17:00<br />\n<br />\n然後同一位朋友再聯絡我：「叫人去留意下體育館先，主要明日六個地區體育館。相信今晚4am後會有動靜。<br />\n估計偽解放軍入住體育館及作臨時大量示威者被拘捕之用。」<br />\n自行判斷 20190930 17:59<br />\n<br />\n半小時後有另一朋友因看到我fb的兩個post，打電話給我：「唔止運動場/ 體育館，包括民政署的社區會堂/中心都有，麻煩通知手足」（這位朋友本身做的工作屬保安性質）<br />\n<br />\n #港島手足留意跑馬地某社區會堂"},{"pid":"564462405ece5bf14fa843baf3c118a30b910a0e","tid":1606942,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:41:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"639c59f4225ef199e079097a82be97034b52ff7f","tid":1606942,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:42:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f39134de5ee386bbccf017da510e94b305ba1717","tid":1606942,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:43:51.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"5167465f9f063317428a4737f83995ddd111e1bf","tid":1606942,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:44:37.000Z","msg":"Reasonable speculation <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"108c760d8400e03f3b19e24e7b6d5c8e97a81ef6","tid":1606942,"uid":34920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:46:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid